\s ABWIRA ABIGISHWA BIWE ATI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Abwir\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd Abigishwa biwe ati: Ntimukiganyir’ amagara kuvyo muzorya\bd*\bd ,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd {\bd*\bd cank\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  imibiri kuvyo muzokwambara.\bd*\bd } x2\bd*
\pc \bdit Nimwitegereze ibikona vyose\bdit*\bdit ,\bdit*\bdit  ingene bitabiba ntibishwabure\bdit*\bdit ,\bdit*\bdit  ntibigir’ububiko cank’ikigega\bdit*\bdit ,\bdit*\bdit  {kand’Imana Irabitunga\bdit*\bdit .\bdit*\bdit } x2\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Erega mwebwe muruta ibisiga, ninde muri mwebwe yoshobozwa,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd n\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd amaganya gusumvy\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd uko yareha\bd*\bd ,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd {\bd*\bd nk’ukuboko kumwe gusa\bd*\bd .} x2\bd*
\pc \bdit Nuko nimutashobora gukora igito gose? Ni iki gituma mwiganyira ibindi vyose? Nimwitegereze amashurwe uko akura, {Ntiyirirw’ aratama ntajish’impuzu.} x2 Ariko ndababwira ko na Salomo, mu bwiza bwiwe bwose yahawe, {ntiyar\bdit*\bdit ’\bdit*\bdit ashajije nka rimwe muri yo.} x2\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Non’Imana ko yambik’ ivyatsi ku misozi\bd*\bd ,\bd*\bd  birih’uyu mus’ejo bigaturirwa, mbega ntizorushiriza kubambika, {mwebwe abo ukwizera guke?} x2\bd*
\pc \bdit Kandi ntimukitwararike kurya no kunywa, ntimukiganyire kuko ivyo vyose, abanyamahanga bavyitwararika, {ariko So arazi kw’ivyo mubikena\bdit*\bdit .\bdit*\bdit } x2 Ariko mwitwararik’ Ubwami bwiwe, {nih’ivyo vyose muzovyongerwa.} x2\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe mwa busho buto ntimutinye\bd*\bd ,\bd*\bd  kuko So bimuhimbara kubah\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  Ubwami\bd*\bd .\bd*\bd  Mugure ivyo mufise mutange ibiguzi\bd*\bd , {\bd*\bd vyo\bd*\bd se\bd*\bd  kubw’ubuntu bwa Yesu Kristo\bd*\bd .} x2\bd*
\pc \bdit Mwibaririr’ imifuko idashira, Ubutunzi budashira buri mw’Ijuru, ahatagerwa n’ibisuma n’inyenzi, {kukw’ah’ Ubutunzi bwanyu buri, arih’imitima yanyu izoba} x2\bdit*
